notes.text:
Red Hat OpenShift Builds 1.0.2
Important: Ships the operator with OCP v4.16
notes.title: Topic

notes.text:
The release of Red Hat OpenShift Builds 1.0.2 General Availability provides the following change(s):
- The builds operator is now available on OCP 4.16 clusters.
